      <title>2021【保姆级教程】Manjaro系统美化和软件安装</title>
      <link href="/posts/b24d8571/b24d8571.html"/>
      <url>/posts/b24d8571/b24d8571.html</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="我和manjaro（二）"><a href="#我和manjaro（二）" class="headerlink" title="我和manjaro（二）"></a>我和manjaro（二）</h2><p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/jssdwang06/figure/master/Manjaro/Manjaro%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E7%BE%8E%E5%8C%96/0.png"></p><p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/jssdwang06/figure/master/Manjaro/Manjaro%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E7%BE%8E%E5%8C%96/1.png"></p><p>仿Mac最终成品图</p><h2 id="系统美化："><a href="#系统美化：" class="headerlink" title="系统美化："></a>系统美化：</h2><p>每个人喜好不一样，大家根据自己的喜好进行美化即可。</p><p>包括主题、图标、光标、Shell。</p><h3 id="主题"><a href="#主题" class="headerlink" title="主题"></a>主题</h3><ul><li>在<code>～</code>目录下创建<code>.themes</code>文件夹</li><li>下载<a href="https://www.gnome-look.org/p/1403328/">WhiteSur Gtk Theme</a>主题压缩包</li><li>解压主题压缩包到<code>.themes</code>文件夹</li></ul><h3 id="图标"><a href="#图标" class="headerlink" title="图标"></a>图标</h3><ul><li>在<code>～</code>目录下创建<code>.icons</code>文件夹</li><li>下载<a href="https://www.pling.com/s/Gnome/p/1305429">McMojave-circle</a>图标压缩包</li><li>解压图标压缩包到<code>.icons</code>文件夹</li></ul><h3 id="光标"><a href="#光标" class="headerlink" title="光标"></a>光标</h3><ul><li>下载<a href="https://github.com/ful1e5/apple_cursor">macOS Big Sur </a>光标压缩包</li><li>解压光标压缩包到<code>.icons</code>文件夹</li></ul><h3 id="Shell"><a href="#Shell" class="headerlink" title="Shell"></a>Shell</h3><p>刚解压的主题包中已包含<code>Shell</code>主题</p><h3 id="标题栏"><a href="#标题栏" class="headerlink" title="标题栏"></a>标题栏</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">优化（tweak）-&gt;窗口标题栏-&gt;标题栏按钮-&gt;放置-&gt;左</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/jssdwang06/figure/master/Manjaro/Manjaro%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E7%BE%8E%E5%8C%96/7.png"></p><h3 id="美化"><a href="#美化" class="headerlink" title="美化"></a>美化</h3><p>在<code>优化（tweak）-&gt;外观</code>中依次设置即可，可参考我的设置。</p><p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/jssdwang06/figure/master/Manjaro/Manjaro%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E7%BE%8E%E5%8C%96/2.png"></p><h2 id="系统设置"><a href="#系统设置" class="headerlink" title="系统设置"></a>系统设置</h2><h3 id="配置镜像源"><a href="#配置镜像源" class="headerlink" title="配置镜像源"></a>配置镜像源</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">BASH</span><br><span class="line">sudo pacman-mirrors -i -c China -m rank # 更新镜像源排名，选择延迟小的。</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>然后修改<code>/etc/pacman.conf</code>，在最后一行添加：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">BASH</span><br><span class="line">[archlinuxcn]</span><br><span class="line">SigLevel = Optional TrustedOnly </span><br><span class="line">Server = https://mirrors.ustc.edu.cn/archlinuxcn/$arch</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>终端运行以下代码更新镜像源和系统：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">BASH</span><br><span class="line">sudo pacman -Sy archlinuxcn-keyring # 导入密匙</span><br><span class="line">sudo pacman -Syyu # 更新系统</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="单击打开文件"><a href="#单击打开文件" class="headerlink" title="单击打开文件"></a>单击打开文件</h3><p>打开<code>文件</code>点击右上角的三个点选择<code>首选项</code></p><p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/jssdwang06/figure/master/Manjaro/Manjaro%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E7%BE%8E%E5%8C%96/3.png"></p><p>选择<code>Single click</code>即可</p><p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/jssdwang06/figure/master/Manjaro/Manjaro%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E7%BE%8E%E5%8C%96/4.png"></p><h3 id="更改grub引导界面"><a href="#更改grub引导界面" class="headerlink" title="更改grub引导界面"></a>更改grub引导界面</h3><blockquote><p>GNU GRUB（GRand Unified Bootloader简称“GRUB”）是一个多操作系统启动程序，它允许用户可以在计算机内同时拥有多个操作系统，并在计算机启动时选择希望运行的操作系统。</p></blockquote><p>自带的grub有点丑，且分辨率还比较低，在<a href="https://www.gnome-look.org/browse/cat/109/ord/rating/">Grub Themes</a>下载自己喜欢的主题，这里我下载的是<code>Grub-theme-vimix</code>，下载好后解压，进入解压后的目录执行以下安装命令：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">BASH</span><br><span class="line">sudo sh install.sh</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>稍等片刻即可安装成功，重启后发现引导界面已成功更改。</p><p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/jssdwang06/figure/master/Manjaro/Manjaro%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E7%BE%8E%E5%8C%96/8.png"></p><h3 id="为terminal设置快捷键"><a href="#为terminal设置快捷键" class="headerlink" title="为terminal设置快捷键"></a>为<code>terminal</code>设置快捷键</h3><p>打开<code>设置-&gt;键盘快捷键</code>，找到自定义快捷键，点击<code>+</code>，设置如下：</p><p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/jssdwang06/figure/master/Manjaro/Manjaro%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E7%BE%8E%E5%8C%96/5.png"></p><h2 id="软件包管理器"><a href="#软件包管理器" class="headerlink" title="软件包管理器"></a>软件包管理器</h2><h3 id="pacman"><a href="#pacman" class="headerlink" title="pacman"></a><code>pacman</code></h3><p>用 C 语言编写的软件包管理器，安装需要加<code>sudo</code></p><p>详细使用方法请参考<a href="https://wiki.archlinux.org/title/Pacman_(%E7%AE%80%E4%BD%93%E4%B8%AD%E6%96%87)#%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E8%BD%AF%E4%BB%B6%E5%8C%85">pacman</a></p><table><thead><tr><th>命令</th><th>描述</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>sudo pacman -S</td><td>安装或升级单个软件包</td></tr><tr><td>sudo pacman -Syu</td><td>升级软件包和整个系统</td></tr><tr><td>sudo pacman -R</td><td>删除单个软件包保留依赖</td></tr><tr><td>sudo pacman -Rsu</td><td>删除软件包和所有依赖</td></tr><tr><td>sudo pacman -Scc</td><td>删除缓存中的全部文件</td></tr><tr><td>sudo pacman -Qs</td><td>查询已安装的软件包</td></tr></tbody></table><h3 id="yay"><a href="#yay" class="headerlink" title="yay"></a><code>yay</code></h3><p>用 Go 编写的 AUR 助手，安装不需要加<code>sudo</code>。</p><p>详细使用方式请参考<a href="https://github.com/Jguer/yay">yay</a></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">BASH</span><br><span class="line">sudo pacman -S yay</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><table><thead><tr><th>命令</th><th>描述</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>yay -S</td><td>安装包</td></tr><tr><td>yay -Rns</td><td>删除包</td></tr><tr><td>yay -Qi</td><td>查询安装的版本</td></tr><tr><td>yay -Pc</td><td>打印系统统计信息</td></tr><tr><td>yay -Syu</td><td>升级所有已安装的包</td></tr><tr><td>yay -Yc</td><td>清除不需要的依赖项</td></tr></tbody></table><h2 id="常用软件："><a href="#常用软件：" class="headerlink" title="常用软件："></a>常用软件：</h2><p>每个人使用的场景不同，以下软件按需安装即可。</p><p>为避免接下来安装过程中提示<code>Cannot find the strip binary required for object fil...</code>，先安装 <code>fakeroot、binutils</code> 等打包基本工具。</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">BASH</span><br><span class="line">sudo pacman -S base-devel</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="中文输入法"><a href="#中文输入法" class="headerlink" title="中文输入法"></a>中文输入法</h3><p>先安装<code>fcitix5</code>全家桶（fcitx5，fcitx5-qt，fcitx5-gtk，fcitx5-configtool）。</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">BASH</span><br><span class="line">sudo pacman -S fcitx5-im</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>再安装中文支持</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">BASH</span><br><span class="line">sudo pacman -S fcitx5-chinese-addons</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>配置环境</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">BASH</span><br><span class="line">vi ~/.pam_environment</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>写入以下内容</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">BASH</span><br><span class="line">INPUT_METHOD  DEFAULT=fcitx5</span><br><span class="line">GTK_IM_MODULE DEFAULT=fcitx5</span><br><span class="line">QT_IM_MODULE  DEFAULT=fcitx5</span><br><span class="line">XMODIFIERS    DEFAULT=\@im=fcitx5</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>重启电脑，点击右上角输入法选择设置，添加拼音，点击OK即可。</p><p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/jssdwang06/figure/master/Manjaro/Manjaro%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E7%BE%8E%E5%8C%96/10.png"></p><p>输入法切换：<code>Ctrl</code> + <code>Shift</code>，在中文输入法下可以用<code>Left Shift</code>切换到英文。</p><h3 id="Vim"><a href="#Vim" class="headerlink" title="Vim"></a><code>Vim</code></h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">BASH</span><br><span class="line">yay -S vim</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="zsh"><a href="#zsh" class="headerlink" title="zsh"></a><code>zsh</code></h3><h4 id="查看系统所有shell"><a href="#查看系统所有shell" class="headerlink" title="查看系统所有shell"></a>查看系统所有<code>shell</code></h4><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">BASH</span><br><span class="line">cat /etc/shells</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="更改默认shell为zsh"><a href="#更改默认shell为zsh" class="headerlink" title="更改默认shell为zsh"></a>更改默认<code>shell</code>为<code>zsh</code></h4><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">BASH</span><br><span class="line">chsh -s /usr/bin/zsh</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="安装ohmyzsh"><a href="#安装ohmyzsh" class="headerlink" title="安装ohmyzsh"></a>安装<code>ohmyzsh</code></h4><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">BASH</span><br><span class="line">wget https://github.com/robbyrussell/oh-my-zsh/raw/master/tools/install.sh -O - | sh</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="安装插件"><a href="#安装插件" class="headerlink" title="安装插件"></a>安装插件</h4><h5 id="zsh-syntax-highlighting：语法高亮"><a href="#zsh-syntax-highlighting：语法高亮" class="headerlink" title="zsh-syntax-highlighting：语法高亮"></a><code>zsh-syntax-highlighting</code>：语法高亮</h5><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">BASH</span><br><span class="line">git clone https://github.com/zsh-users/zsh-syntax-highlighting.git $&#123;ZSH_CUSTOM&#125;/plugins/zsh-syntax-highlighting</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h5 id="autosuggestions：记住用过的命令"><a href="#autosuggestions：记住用过的命令" class="headerlink" title="autosuggestions：记住用过的命令"></a><code>autosuggestions</code>：记住用过的命令</h5><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">BASH</span><br><span class="line">git clone git://github.com/zsh-users/zsh-autosuggestions ~/.oh-my-zsh/custom/plugins/zsh-autosuggestions</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="修改主题"><a href="#修改主题" class="headerlink" title="修改主题"></a>修改主题</h4><p>这里使用的主题是<code>powerlevel10k</code>，详细信息可从<a href="https://github.com/romkatv/powerlevel10k">Github</a>找到。</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">BASH</span><br><span class="line">git clone --depth=1 https://github.com/romkatv/powerlevel10k.git $&#123;ZSH_CUSTOM:-~/.oh-my-zsh/custom&#125;/themes/powerlevel10k</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="修改配置文件"><a href="#修改配置文件" class="headerlink" title="修改配置文件"></a>修改配置文件</h4><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">BASH</span><br><span class="line">sudo vim ~/.zshrc</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>详情参考以下内容</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">BASH</span><br><span class="line">#更改ZSH_THEME</span><br><span class="line">ZSH_THEME=&quot;powerlevel10k/powerlevel10k&quot;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">#更改plugins</span><br><span class="line">plugins=(git</span><br><span class="line">      zsh-autosuggestions</span><br><span class="line">      zsh-syntax-highlighting</span><br><span class="line">    )</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">#刷新配置</span><br><span class="line">source ~/.zshrc</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">#打开终端按提示进行配置即可</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/jssdwang06/figure/master/Manjaro/Manjaro%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E7%BE%8E%E5%8C%96/26.png"></p><h3 id="安装Typora"><a href="#安装Typora" class="headerlink" title="安装Typora"></a>安装<code>Typora</code></h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">BASH</span><br><span class="line">yay -S typora</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="安装Notion"><a href="#安装Notion" class="headerlink" title="安装Notion"></a>安装<code>Notion</code></h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">BASH</span><br><span class="line">yay -S notion-app</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="安装Atom"><a href="#安装Atom" class="headerlink" title="安装Atom"></a>安装<code>Atom</code></h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">BASH</span><br><span class="line">yay -S atom</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="安装Vscode"><a href="#安装Vscode" class="headerlink" title="安装Vscode"></a>安装<code>Vscode</code></h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">BASH</span><br><span class="line">yay -S visual-studio-code-bin</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="安装Picgo"><a href="#安装Picgo" class="headerlink" title="安装Picgo"></a>安装<code>Picgo</code></h3><p>配合<code>Github</code>搭建图床</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">BASH</span><br><span class="line">yay -S picgo-appimage</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="安装Okular"><a href="#安装Okular" class="headerlink" title="安装Okular"></a>安装<code>Okular</code></h3><p>PDF阅读器</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">BASH</span><br><span class="line">yay -S okular</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="安装网易云"><a href="#安装网易云" class="headerlink" title="安装网易云"></a>安装<code>网易云</code></h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">MARKDOWN</span><br><span class="line">yay -S netease-cloud-music</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="安装Spotify"><a href="#安装Spotify" class="headerlink" title="安装Spotify"></a>安装<code>Spotify</code></h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">BASH</span><br><span class="line">yay -S spotify</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="安装flame截图"><a href="#安装flame截图" class="headerlink" title="安装flame截图"></a>安装<code>flame截图</code></h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">MARKDOWN</span><br><span class="line">yay -S flameshot</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="设置flameshot："><a href="#设置flameshot：" class="headerlink" title="设置flameshot："></a>设置<code>flameshot</code>：</h4><p>打开<code>flameshot</code>设置页</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">CODE</span><br><span class="line">flameshot config</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>按自己的需要调整即可，这里我取消了铅笔、直线、实心矩形等。</p><p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/jssdwang06/figure/master/Manjaro/Manjaro%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E7%BE%8E%E5%8C%96/11.png"></p><h4 id="设置快捷键"><a href="#设置快捷键" class="headerlink" title="设置快捷键"></a>设置快捷键</h4><p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/jssdwang06/figure/master/Manjaro/Manjaro%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E7%BE%8E%E5%8C%96/12.png"></p><h3 id="安装Chrome"><a href="#安装Chrome" class="headerlink" title="安装Chrome"></a>安装<code>Chrome</code></h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">BASH</span><br><span class="line">yay -S google-chrome</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>当我们打开Chrome时发现，发现标题栏会显得很突兀</p><p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/jssdwang06/figure/master/Manjaro/Manjaro%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E7%BE%8E%E5%8C%96/13.png"></p><p>这时我们只需要，右键标签栏空白处勾选使用系统标题栏和边框即可。</p><p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/jssdwang06/figure/master/Manjaro/Manjaro%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E7%BE%8E%E5%8C%96/14.png"></p><h3 id="安装XDM"><a href="#安装XDM" class="headerlink" title="安装XDM"></a>安装<code>XDM</code></h3><p>去<a href="https://xtremedownloadmanager.com/#downloads">XDM官网</a>下载最新版本的安装包（目前最新版本为7.2.11），解压后进入解压目录在终端中执行安装命令：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">BASH</span><br><span class="line">su -c ./install.sh  </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>安装完成打开<code>XDM</code>，按照提示安装对应浏览器扩展即可，默认下载到<code>/home/用户名/Downloads</code>。</p><h3 id="安装Edge"><a href="#安装Edge" class="headerlink" title="安装Edge"></a>安装<code>Edge</code></h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">BASH</span><br><span class="line">yay -S microsoft-edge-dev-bin</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="安装anki"><a href="#安装anki" class="headerlink" title="安装anki"></a>安装<code>anki</code></h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">BASH</span><br><span class="line">yay -S anki</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="安装xmind2020"><a href="#安装xmind2020" class="headerlink" title="安装xmind2020"></a>安装<code>xmind2020</code></h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">BASH</span><br><span class="line">yay -S xmind-2020</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="安装微信"><a href="#安装微信" class="headerlink" title="安装微信"></a>安装<code>微信</code></h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">BASH</span><br><span class="line">yay -S deepin-wine-wechat</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>切换到<code>deepin-wine</code></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">BASH</span><br><span class="line">/opt/apps/com.qq.weixin.deepin/files/run.sh -d</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="安装teams"><a href="#安装teams" class="headerlink" title="安装teams"></a>安装<code>teams</code></h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">BASH</span><br><span class="line">yay -S teams</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="安装blechbit"><a href="#安装blechbit" class="headerlink" title="安装blechbit"></a>安装<code>blechbit</code></h3><p>清理磁盘空间</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">BASH</span><br><span class="line">yay -S bleachbit</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="安装Albert"><a href="#安装Albert" class="headerlink" title="安装Albert"></a>安装<code>Albert</code></h3><p>软件启动器</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">BASH</span><br><span class="line">yay -S albert</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="软件设置："><a href="#软件设置：" class="headerlink" title="软件设置："></a>软件设置：</h4><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Hotkey`为更改快捷键为`Ctrl+空格</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>勾选 <code>Autostart on login</code>：开机自启</p><p>在<code>Extensions</code>里勾选所需要的部件，我这里勾选的是<code>Applications</code>，<code>Files</code>，<code>System</code>，<code>WebSearch</code></p><p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/jssdwang06/figure/master/Manjaro/Manjaro%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E7%BE%8E%E5%8C%96/15.png"></p><p>最后按需设置<code>WebSearch</code>里的搜索引擎，可以参考下图我的设置。</p><p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/jssdwang06/figure/master/Manjaro/Manjaro%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E7%BE%8E%E5%8C%96/16.png"></p><h4 id="使用方式："><a href="#使用方式：" class="headerlink" title="使用方式："></a>使用方式：</h4><p>比如我们想在<code>Github</code>里面搜索<code>numpy</code>，我们只需要以下三步：</p><ol><li>快捷键<code>Ctrl+空格</code>启动<code>Albert</code>搜索框。</li><li>在搜索框中输入<code>git numpy</code>（注意中间有个空格）。<br><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/jssdwang06/figure/master/Manjaro/Manjaro%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E7%BE%8E%E5%8C%96/17.png"></li><li>回车即可自动打开浏览器，跳转GitHub界面。</li></ol><p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/jssdwang06/figure/master/Manjaro/Manjaro%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E7%BE%8E%E5%8C%96/18.png"></p><h3 id="安装Easystroke"><a href="#安装Easystroke" class="headerlink" title="安装Easystroke"></a>安装<code>Easystroke</code></h3><p>鼠标手势，(顺便推荐Win下的<code>MouseInc</code>)</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">BASH</span><br><span class="line">yay -S easystroke</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="软件设置"><a href="#软件设置" class="headerlink" title="软件设置"></a>软件设置</h4><p>默认按键为鼠标<code>中键</code>（<code>Button2</code>）这里更改成了鼠标<code>右键</code>（<code>Button3</code>），勾选<code>Autostart easystroke</code>开机自启动，在返回到<code>Actions</code>按需添加手势即可。</p><p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/jssdwang06/figure/master/Manjaro/Manjaro%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E7%BE%8E%E5%8C%96/19.png"></p><h4 id="常用手势"><a href="#常用手势" class="headerlink" title="常用手势"></a>常用手势</h4><p>按需设置即可，同时附上我设置的手势，Super键是左下角win键）。<br><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/jssdwang06/figure/master/Manjaro/Manjaro%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E7%BE%8E%E5%8C%96/20.png"></p><h3 id="安装Wps"><a href="#安装Wps" class="headerlink" title="安装Wps"></a>安装<code>Wps</code></h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">MARKDOWN</span><br><span class="line">#避免安装完后打开Wps提示字体不存在，这里建议先安装字体</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">#安装字体</span><br><span class="line">yay -S wps-office wps-office-mui-zh-cn wps-office-fonts ttf-wps-fonts </span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">#安装Times new roman字体</span><br><span class="line">yay -S ttf-ms-fonts</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">#安装wps</span><br><span class="line">yay -S wps-office-cn</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="安装Latex"><a href="#安装Latex" class="headerlink" title="安装Latex"></a>安装Latex</h3><p>目前已转在线的Overleaf，开箱即用。</p><p>还没有注册的小伙伴，快点击<a href="https://www.overleaf.com/?r=2b6dc4e3&rm=d&rs=b">链接</a>进行注册吧。</p><p>以下安装过程亦可放心食用。</p><hr><h4 id="安装图形化安装界面"><a href="#安装图形化安装界面" class="headerlink" title="安装图形化安装界面"></a>安装图形化安装界面</h4><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">BASH</span><br><span class="line">yay -S tk</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="挂载ISO"><a href="#挂载ISO" class="headerlink" title="挂载ISO"></a>挂载<code>ISO</code></h4><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">BASH</span><br><span class="line">sudo mount -o loop /path/to/texlive2020.iso /mnt</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>如果提示：mount: &#x2F;mnt: 警告：设备写保护，使用只读方式挂载，忽略即可。</p><h4 id="安装"><a href="#安装" class="headerlink" title="安装"></a>安装</h4><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">BASH</span><br><span class="line">cd /mnt</span><br><span class="line">sudo ./install-tl--gui</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>去除不需要的语言和<code>TeXworks editor</code>，点击安装</p><p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/jssdwang06/figure/master/Manjaro/Manjaro%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E7%BE%8E%E5%8C%96/21.png"></p><p>安装时间会有点长，请耐心等待安装完成。</p><h4 id="添加环境变量"><a href="#添加环境变量" class="headerlink" title="添加环境变量"></a>添加环境变量</h4><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">BASH</span><br><span class="line">sudo vim ~/.zshrc</span><br><span class="line"># 在文件末尾添加</span><br><span class="line">export MANPATH=/usr/local/texlive/2020/texmf-dist/doc/man:$MANPATH </span><br><span class="line">export INFOPATH=/usr/local/texlive/2020/texmf-dist/doc/info:$INFOPATH</span><br><span class="line">export PATH=/usr/local/texlive/2020/bin/x86_64-linux:$PATH</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="测试环境变量"><a href="#测试环境变量" class="headerlink" title="测试环境变量"></a>测试环境变量</h4><p>在终端输入：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">BASH</span><br><span class="line">tex --version</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/jssdwang06/figure/master/Manjaro/Manjaro%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E7%BE%8E%E5%8C%96/22.png"></p><p>或者</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">TEX</span><br><span class="line">tex &#x27;\empty Hello world!\bye&#x27;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>输出以下内容即生效</p><p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/jssdwang06/figure/master/Manjaro/Manjaro%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E7%BE%8E%E5%8C%96/23.png"></p><h4 id="设置清华镜像为更新源"><a href="#设置清华镜像为更新源" class="headerlink" title="设置清华镜像为更新源"></a>设置清华镜像为更新源</h4><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">BASH</span><br><span class="line">sudo tlmgr option repository https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/CTAN/systems/texlive/tlnet</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="更新tlmgr和宏包"><a href="#更新tlmgr和宏包" class="headerlink" title="更新tlmgr和宏包"></a>更新tlmgr和宏包</h4><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">BASH</span><br><span class="line">sudo tlmgr update --self --all</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="编译俄语报错"><a href="#编译俄语报错" class="headerlink" title="编译俄语报错"></a>编译俄语报错</h4><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Package fontspec: The font &quot;CMU Serif&quot; cannot be found.</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>需要下载<a href="https://sourceforge.net/projects/cm-unicode/">Computer Modern Unicode fonts</a>字体，安装完成后更新字体缓存，即可正常编译。</p><p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/jssdwang06/figure/master/Manjaro/Manjaro%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E7%BE%8E%E5%8C%96/24.png"></p><h4 id="安装字体"><a href="#安装字体" class="headerlink" title="安装字体"></a>安装字体</h4><p>复制要安装的<code>字体文件（ttf）</code>到<code>/usr/share/fonts/TTF</code>文件夹:</p><p>刷新字体:</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">BASH</span><br><span class="line">fc-cache -fv</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="更新字体缓存"><a href="#更新字体缓存" class="headerlink" title="更新字体缓存"></a>更新字体缓存</h4><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">BASH</span><br><span class="line">cd /usr/share/fonts/ #字体的位置</span><br><span class="line">sudo fc-cache -v -f  #更新缓存</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="Gnome插件"><a href="#Gnome插件" class="headerlink" title="Gnome插件"></a>Gnome插件</h3><p>插件可以在<a href="https://extensions.gnome.org/">Gnome Extensions</a>下载安装</p><p>推荐几个插件</p><ol><li><a href="https://extensions.gnome.org/extension/97/coverflow-alt-tab/">Coverflow Alt-Tab</a> 切换应用效果美化</li><li><a href="https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https://extensions.gnome.org/extension/104/netspeed/">NetSpeed</a> 显示实时网速</li><li><a href="https://extensions.gnome.org/extension/3210/compiz-windows-effect/">Compiz windows effect</a> 窗口切换效果</li><li><a href="https://extensions.gnome.org/extension/2/move-clock/">Frippery Move Clock</a>将时钟位置向右移动</li><li><a href="https://extensions.gnome.org/extension/1319/gsconnect/">GsConnect</a> Pc手机协同工具，详细使用方法请参考<a href="https://userbase.kde.org/KDE_Connect/Tutorials/Useful_commands">Connect使用</a>，也可以参考我的设置：</li></ol><p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/jssdwang06/figure/master/Manjaro/Manjaro%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E7%BE%8E%E5%8C%96/25.png"></p><h2 id="参考"><a href="#参考" class="headerlink" title="参考"></a>参考</h2><p><a href="https://cubercsl.cn/configuration/manjaro.html">Manjaro KDE 瞎折腾</a></p><p><a href="https://juejin.cn/post/6844903779981082638">Manjaro 美化与调优</a></p><p><a href="https://oscarcx123.github.io/tech/manjaro-xfce-setup.html#Win10%E6%9B%B4%E6%96%B0%E5%90%8E%E4%BF%AE%E5%A4%8Dgrub">Manjaro XFCE 安装和调教</a></p><p><a href="https://www.blurredcode.com/2020/08/linux%E4%B8%8Btexlive%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E6%8C%87%E5%8C%97/">Manjaro下texlive环境配置指北</a></p><h2 id="结语"><a href="#结语" class="headerlink" title="结语"></a>结语</h2><p>至此，我们已经完成了系统的美化和常用软件的安装，本篇教程也到此结束了。</p><p>下篇文章会介绍如何在<code>Manjaro</code>下搭建<code>hexo</code>个人博客，那让我们下次见咯～</p><p>最后，感谢你看到这里！</p>]]></content>
      
      
